Welcome into this place,
You are welcome
Into this broken vessel.
You inhabit all the praises
Of your people,

So we lift our hands
And we lift our hearts
And we offer up
our praises unto You.

Welcome into this place,
You are welcome
Into this broken vessel.
You inhabit all the praises
Of your people,

So we lift our hands,
And we lift our hearts,
And we offer up our praise
Unto Your Name.

